title: Let's Watch TV: Great Brittish Baking Show
description:
This week, Mama Fran's english accent needs work and Joe get's an insatiable craving for Focaccia Bread as they watch the classic Brittish reality show The Great Brittish Bake-Off. Then they finish the show off with a fantastic Wild Story Wednesday!
